cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the download statistics of EPL publications, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The classification of individual papers based on their download behavior also involves statistical analysis (cs.ST) and potentially machine learning (cs.LG). The study of attractiveness and aging of publications can also be related to social networks (cs.SI) and cryptography (cs.CR).
